ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of JUDITH BAXTER of Clifton Royal, New Brunswick, as a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of Civilization to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Thelma Ann Brennan.
